version_description:
- English version is available
- 3 save slots are available to use now
Added online save feature for persistent save after uninstalling or for cross-device playing

New features: BABY QUESTS!
Build children furniture, help your wife through pregnancy with cravings, doctor checkups and hospital trips with new extensive baby storyline and quest with all-new CG scenes . Unlock your cute baby at the end of the quest!

- Added laundry building to help you when you lost your quest item
- Fixed a bug where you can get trash even though you don't have gloves yet and the trash is not marked
- Fixed bug where you can not go to work even though you completed all the requirements
- Other minor adjustments
iOS specific fix about online save cannot be loaded, fixed

We remade the engine for this version!* 3 new girls to know, date, marry and have family with: Citra, Jessica and Tasya
* A new area with all new buildings in it.
A lot more things! See this list for the detail:
http://ikanasinproduction.com/citampistories/releaseLog_english.html
